author: uhussain
body: Deleting unnecessary assignments to variables flagged by the static analyzer. The code changes have been discussed and tests performed do not raise any conflicts or errors.
title: Fixing static analyzer warnings in CosmicClusterAlgo.cc, PreshowerClusterAlgo.cc, PreshowerPhiClusterAlgo.cc ,EcalClusterEnergyCorrectionObjectSpecific.cc and SiStripElectronAlgo.cc
